**Problems:**
1. Structures (ID >= 64,000,000) are never resolved - they require auth token
2. Solar system IDs (~30,000,000 range) are never resolved
3. No caching - same location gets resolved repeatedly
4. Item IDs (assets inside containers) can't be resolved as locations

